# Core ADR Trigger

Goal: Force explicit decisions on high-risk changes.

- Write ADR before coding if change affects:
  - architecture boundaries
  - data model
  - runtime (node/edge)
  - auth/RBAC
  - billing/entitlements
  - multi-tenancy isolation
  - data export/delete
- ADR must list: decision, options, tradeoffs, consequences
- Use template: `docs/adr/0001-template.md`
- ADR number format: `NNNN-<short-name>.md` (sequential)
- Document rejected alternatives and why
